proof_script:
lemma bind_cong [fundef_cong]: fixes m1 :: "('t, 'a) gen_parser" assumes "m1 ts2 = m2 ts2" and "\<And> y ts. m2 ts2 = Inr (y, ts) \<Longrightarrow> f1 y ts = f2 y ts" and "ts1 = ts2" shows "((m1 \<bind> f1) ts1) = ((m2 \<bind> f2) ts2)"
using assms
unfolding bind_def
by (auto intro: bind_cong[OF refl])
